{"tid":309250,"cid":14,"subCid":0,"title":"月光族揮手區","createTime":"2017-07-05T00:41:45.000Z","updateTime":"2017-07-06T06:30:49.000Z","uid":58675,"like":9,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"dffa34b7450d1cd31d6c17777881867273f778ab","tid":309250,"uid":58675,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-05T00:41:45.000Z","msg":"等出糧就等一個月...<br />\n唔駛5mins就清袋...（卡數...生活費）<br />\n剛出門時同老婆講話夜晚想找多份兼職 例如倉務咁...當然唔贊成...話小左時間陪佢同小朋友...我知<br />\n但每個月真係無錢用...真係要用就靠碌卡（我知唔健康...但生活迫人無計<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ）...我知生活都係要過...唯有繼續硬著頭皮撐落去...坐巴士時純粹呻下<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 如有巴打都係咁既情況...共勉之<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"484c18ae5dcc63f0aef7f9dbf2c9949d1c3c1b59","tid":309250,"uid":55296,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-05T00:47:23.000Z","msg":"你老婆有無做嘢？"},{"pid":"519bcfa37c006fe11d0e43e90b26e28f3609fccd","tid":309250,"uid":58675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-05T00:48:19.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>你老婆有無做嘢？</blockquote><br />\n無<br />\n全職揍小朋友"},{"pid":"8bea841ac5427853cb9e237434ff5fcdc6b88c7d","tid":309250,"uid":20020,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-05T00:49:45.000Z","msg":"收入幾多<br />\n做邊行"},{"pid":"b8c25498ed7dd989473b8e3737ea0a4d9ae5f826","tid":309250,"uid":58675,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-05T00:52:38.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>收入幾多<br />\n做邊行</blockquote><br />\n砌稿佬 20K<br />\n過多幾年四章了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e79278f8614f3edceb474305ae83dbf559963a93","tid":309250,"uid":55614,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-05T00:53:02.000Z","msg":"轉工<br />\n要借都唔好禁卡借"},{"pid":"56123e477b2ec68017b6d1b545f2a5e5f90da984","tid":309250,"uid":12291,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-05T00:54:00.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"f833d7cd4ca8ba